node.text: Opportunity of a lifetime! @311rsmotorsport and @porschemotorsportnorthamerica tossed me the keys to their 992 cup car here at BIR to turn some laps! Always dreamed of driving a Porsche racecar … let alone the latest and greatest! Carrera cup is here in the USA for the first time ever and 23 of these factory racecars battle head to head! This car is 1 of 2 that @311rs runs - driven by @lehmank and @ryangates . Can’t wait for you guys to see the video!

node.text: In honor of 7’s day, I thought I would drop the big news! @rx7vargas put this thing together for me MONTHS ago and it’s been patiently waiting for the right chassis - and for us to get some time. I’ve been dead set on this being the first big project after moving, but didn’t want to dive in until we were properly settled into the new shop. Beyond stoked to tear into this thing and start a new journey with my vision of the perfect NA 4 rotor street car. Check out my new video for all the details! 💛💛💛 #lzmfg
